cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it proposes an image caption system that aligns visual perception with language generation. The paper also introduces novel modeling techniques, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper benchmarks its system and compares it to published results, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR).
